---
title: Eastern European-Inspired Beyond Meat® Piroshki  with Chive Sour Cream
description: Piroshki are delightful – they're golden pockets of joy filled with a savoury mix of Beyond Meat®, onions and spices, all wrapped in a pillowy soft dough. These scrumptious pastries can be baked or fried to perfection, delivering a burst of flavour with every bite. Perfect for any occasion, enjoy them warm with a dollop of sour cream for an extra zing.

Ingredients: Pizza dough (enriched wheat flour (wheat flour, niacin, reduced iron, ascorbic acid, thiamine mononitrate, riboflavin, amylase, folic acid), water, semolina, canola oil, sugar, yeast, salt, calcium propionate, sodium stearoyl-2- lactylate, calcium sulphate) (wheat) • Plant-based burger patty (water, pea protein, canola oil, flavour, refined coconut oil, rice protein, dried yeast, cocoa butter, methylcellulose, potato starch, apple extract, potassium chloride, salt, vinegar, concentrated lemon juice, beet juice extract (vegetable glycerin, water, ascorbic acid, beet extract, maltodextrin), pomegranate extract, sunflower lecithin, vitamins and minerals (niacin, pyridoxine hydrochloride, thiamine hydrochloride, riboflavin, cyanocobalamin, calcium pantothenate, ferric orthophosphate, zinc sulphate)) • Carrots • Sour cream (milk ingredients, modified milk ingredients, modified cornstarch, sodium phosphate, sodium citrate, carrageenan, locust bean gum, guar gum, microbial enzyme, bacterial culture) (milk) • Green cabbage • Yellow onion • Grade A egg • Red wine vinegar (wine vinegar, potassium sorbate, sulphites) (sulphites) • Chives • Garlic • Smoked paprika-garlic blend (smoked paprika, garlic powder, silicon dioxide) (sulphites) • Dill-garlic spice blend (dehydrated onion, dehydrated garlic, salt, dill weed, canola oil, silicon dioxide) (sulphites).
